3. Bucket Name: "banners"
4. Public bucket: ✓ AÇIK
5. "Create bucket" butonuna tıkla

ADIM 3: ADMIN PANELİNDEN BANNER YÜKLE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
